{"tid":1507621,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［突發］海關禁店鋪出售激光筆","createTime":"2019-08-26T08:34:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T12:06:17.000Z","uid":216992,"like":4,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"2e7feb15bb9ec32a13441d0ac6cb0a4cf98ae352","tid":1507621,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T08:34:35.000Z","msg":"海關在深水埗一間店舖檢獲13枝懷疑不安全激光筆，並發出禁制通知書，禁止繼續出售，調查仍在進行中。海關表示，有關店舖違反《消費品安全條例》及其附屬法例，於是在上星期五採取行動。海關表示，在今年3月進行試購行動，從一間零售店舖購買一款激光筆進行安全測試，並勒令該店將該款共13枝沒有標示雙語警告或警誡的激光筆儲存於指定的地方。測試結果顯示，該款激光筆沒有裝配相關安全控制裝置，同時亦只附有英文使用警告。海關提醒市民，由於該類激光筆所發出的光束，有機會損害眼睛和皮膚，在任何情況下都不應讓激光筆照射出的光點，射向眼睛。<br />\n<br />\n2019-08-26 16:28:45"},{"pid":"21f0852d3426b26b3b84d76e71652e9e6a35c332","tid":1507621,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T08:34:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f18896d02ebf32ce372ad620453ebd2f1deddc","tid":1507621,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T08:35:09.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY5LurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=c8c82b69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"32153e5971f478940744983e94ad024f83d1ea6f","tid":1507621,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T08:35:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":